English: Alan Shepard was born in New Hampshire, home of the purple finch. He served as a crew member of the Apollo 14, a NASA operated mission. The US Navy awarded Alan Shepard the Distinguished Service Medal, which ranks higher than Department of Commerce Gold Medal.

Maltese: Aleksandr Chumakov twieled fl-1948.
English: Aleksandr Chumakov was born in the year 1948.

Maltese: Abraham A. Ribicoff, kien il-Gvernatur ta’ Connecticut, il-konjuġi tiegħu kien Casey Ribicoff, li twieled fi Chicago.
English: Abraham A. Ribicoff, was the Governor of Connecticut, his spouse was Casey Ribicoff, who was born in Chicago.

Maltese: Aleksander Barkov Jr twieled f’Tampere, il-Finlandja fl-1995 u l-klub tiegħu huwa l-Florida Panthers.
English: Aleksander Barkov Jr was born in Tampere, Finland in 1995 and his club is the Florida Panthers.

Maltese: L-Amerikani bojod huma wieħed mill-gruppi etniċi fl-Istati Uniti, pajjiż fejn il-mexxej jissejjaħ il-President u Washington, D.C. huwa l-belt tal-kapital. Joe Biden huwa mexxej politiku fl-Istati Uniti. Il-pajjiż huwa wkoll l-oriġini ta’ Bacon Explosion.
English: White Americans are one of the ethnic groups in the United States, a country where the leader is called the President and Washington, D.C. is the capital city. Joe Biden is a political leader in the U.S. The country is also the origin of Bacon Explosion.
